                       </div>\n                            <p class=\"text mb-8\">Bng vic k tn di y, i Tc xc nhn: (i) c y  nng lc hnh vi dn s; (ii)  c, hiu, c t vn v hon ton ng  vi (a) ni dung ca Hp ng cho vay vn <span class=\"bold\">(Hp ng)</span>, (b) cc quy nh, th tc c lin quan khi thc hin giao dch cho KAFI vay vn <span class=\"bold\">(Giao Dch)</span>, ng k tin ch, (c) cc quy nh ti B iu khon v iu kin ca Hp ng, (d) Chnh sch x l d liu c nhn, (e) iu khon v iu kin ng k v s dng dch v chng thc ch k s FPT-CA v (f) tt c cc sa i, b sung tng thi k ca cc vn bn ny c KAFI cng b trn trang thng tin in t https://www.kafi.vn; (iii) tnh chnh xc, trung thc, y  ca cc thng tin m i Tc cung cp cho KAFI; (iv) KAFI  cng b cho i Tc bit trc v ri ro c th xy ra khi giao dch cho vay vn trc tuyn, nhng xung t li ich co th pht sinh gia KAFI va i Tc.</p>\n                            <p class=\"text mb-8\">Hp ng c lp thnh 02 (hai) bn ting Vit c gi tr php l nh nhau, mi Bn gi 01 (mt) bn.</p>\n thng nht k kt Hp ng vi cc iu khon v iu kin nh sau: </p>\n                            <h4 class=\"heading2\">B IU KHON V IU KIN CA HP NG </h4>\n                            <table class=\"table-info\" Thng S Khon Cho Vay l mt phn khng tch ri ca Hp ng.</td>\n                                </tr>\n                            </table>\n                            <p class=\"page-now mt-8\">4 | MB-1042.RPM.2025(1)-03 </p>\n                            <div class=\"pagebreak\">&nbsp;</div>\n                            <p class=\"space\">&nbsp;</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"contract-content__page\">\n                            <div class=\"section\">\n                                <h2 class=\"heading1\">iu 2 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Phm vi iu chnh</h2>\n                                <div class=\"text\">\n                                    <p>2.1. KK Chung c p dng cho cc Giao Dch, M i Tc v tt c cc tin ch lin quan m KAFI cung cp cho i Tc ti tng thi im (\"Tin ch Lin Quan\").</p>\n                                    \n                                    <p>2.2. Khi i Tc cho KAFI vay vn, hoc i Tc ng k Tin ch Lin Quan th i Tc mc nhin chp thun tun th KK Chung v cc iu khon v iu kin v tng Tin ch Lin Quan m i Tc s dng (\"KK\"). i Tc hiu rng, KK/KK Chung l mt phn khng tch ri ca Hp ng m i Tc  k vi KAFI v c gi tr php l rng buc gia i Tc v KAFI.</p>\n                                    \n                                    <p>2.3. i Tc  c, hiu r, ng  tun th v chu s rng buc ca KK/KK Chung v cc vn bn/tha thun c lin quan, cng nh cc quy nh, quy ch giao dch khc ca KAFI.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"section\">\n                                <h2 class=\"heading1\">iu 3 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Thng bo</h2>\n                                <div class=\"text\">\n                                    <p>3.1. i Tc ng  rng KAFI s thng bo cho i Tc cc thng tin v Tin ch Lin Quan (bao gm c KK), cc thng tin v quyn li v ngha v ca i Tc v cc thng tin lin quan khc (\"Thng Bo\") thng qua mt trong cc hnh thc sau:</p>\n                                    <ul>\n                                        <li>(i) gi bng ng bu in n a ch lin h m i Tc  ng k;</li>\n                                        <li>(ii) gi tin nhn/gi n s in thoi m i Tc  ng k (tin nhn/cuc gi c th c thc hin thng qua nh mng vin thng hoc thng qua cc ng dng khc m i Tc c ti khon s dng ng dng c ng k bng s in thoi  ng k ti KAFI);</li>\n                                        <li>(iii) gi email n a ch m i Tc  ng k;</li>\n                                        <li>(iv) thng bo trn H Thng GDTT hoc ng trn trang thng tin in t ca KAFI ti a ch https://www.kafi.vn. Bt k hoc tt c cc hnh thc nu trn u c xem l hp l.</li>\n                                    </ul>\n                                    <p>Bt k hoc tt c cc hnh thc nu trn u c xem l hp l.</p>\n\n                                    <p>3.2. Thng Bo c hiu lc p dng k t thi im ghi trong Thng Bo hoc thi im:</p>\n                                    <ul>\n                                        <li>(i) 01 ngy sau khi gi Thng Bo bng hnh thc th bo m n a ch lin h ca i Tc hoc</li>\n                                        <li>(ii) ngay khi KAFI  gi tin nhn, email v/hoc gi in thoi c ghi m cho i Tc;</li>\n                                        <li>(iii) ngay khi KAFI ng Thng Bo trn H Thng GDTT hoc trn trang thng tin in t ca KAFI.</li>\n                                    </ul>\n\n                                    <p>3.3. i Tc c trch nhim duy tr nhng thng tin lin lc  ng k vi KAFI nh: a ch lin h, a ch email, s in thoi,  lun trong tnh trng a ch lin h c th nhn c th chuyn pht, email c th nhn c th in t, s in thoi c th lin h c bt k lc no. i Tc phi ng k thay i thng tin vi KAFI bng vn bn hoc ng k trn H Thng GDTT ngay khi c s thay i. K t thi im KAFI ghi nhn s thay i , lin lc gia Cc Bn s c thc hin thng qua a ch lin h/email/s in thoi mi.</p>\n\n                                    <p>3.4. KAFI khng chu trch nhim trong trng hp i Tc khng duy tr nhng thng tin lin lc  ng k v/hoc khng ng k thay i thng tin kp thi theo quy nh ti khon 3.3 iu ny v/hoc i Tc t  t chi nhn Thng Bo t KAFI. Vic i Tc khng nhn c Thng Bo ca KAFI v nhng l do nu trn khng phi l cn c  KAFI phi hon thc hin cc bin php x l cn thit hoc l cn c  i Tc tr hon thc hin ngha v ca mnh theo quy nh ti Hp ng.</p>\n\n                                    <p>3.5. Trng hp KAFI gi Thng Bo bng ng bu in, chi ph gi th c xem l mt khon thuc Ngha V Thanh Ton ca i Tc theo quyt nh ca KAFI.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"contract-content__page\">\n                            <table class=\"table-info\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n                                <tr>\n                                    <th>iu 4</th>\n                                    <th>Cc iu khon khc  </th>\n                                </tr>\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td>4.1</td>\n                                    <td>Hp ng v nhng ni dung khc lin quan n vic i Tc cho KAFI vay vn nhng khng c  cp trong Hp ng s c gii thch v iu chnh theo quy nh ca php lut Vit Nam.</td>\n                                </tr>\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td>4.2</td>\n                                    <td>Mi tranh chp pht sinh t v/hoc lin quan n Hp ng s c gii quyt thng qua thng lng, ha gii. Trng hp tranh chp khng gii quyt c bng thng lng, ha gii th bt k Bn no cng c quyn a tranh chp ra Trung Tm Trng Ti Quc T Vit Nam bn cnh Phng Thng mi v Cng nghip Vit Nam (\"VIAC\")  gii quyt theo Quy ch t tng trng ti hin hnh ca VIAC. a im tin hnh t tng trng ti l ti Thnh ph H Ch Minh, Vit Nam. Ngn ng tin hnh t tng trng ti l ting Vit. Phn quyt trng ti l chung thm v c gi tr rng buc thc hin i vi Cc Bn.</td>\n                                </tr>\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td>4.3</td>\n                                    <td>Cc Bn cam kt khng thng bo hoc tit l cng khai cc iu khon hoc quy nh ca Hp ng m khng c s chp thun trc bng vn bn ca Bn kia, tr trng hp tit l cho (i) cn b nhn vin, ngi i din, i l, t chc kim ton, bn th ba cung cp Tin ch Lin Quan cho mnh, hoc (ii) c quan Nh nc c thm quyn, hoc (iii) t chc, c nhn khc theo quy nh ca php lut Vit Nam. Quy nh v bo mt ti iu ny vn tip tc c hiu lc sau khi Hp ng chm dt.</td>\n                                </tr>\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td>4.4</td>\n                                    <td>Cc Bn xc nhn rng vic giao kt Hp ng l hon ton t nguyn, khng gi to, khng b p buc, la di, e da, nhm ln. Cc Bn  c li, hiu r quyn, ngha v v li ch hp php ca mnh,  ngha v hu qu php l ca vic giao kt Hp ng.</td>\n                                </tr>\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td>4.5</td>\n                                    <td>i Tc ng  rng KAFI c quyn sa i, b sung hoc iu chnh mt s ni dung ca Hp ng min l cc thay i ny c KAFI thng bo cho i Tc thng qua mt trong cc phng thc quy nh ti iu 3 Hp ng trc khi p dng. Nu i Tc khng c  kin phn i c gi bng vn bn ti KAFI trong thi hn 03 (ba) Ngy Lm Vic k t thi im cc thay i ny c hiu lc hoc tip tc s dng Tin ch Lin Quan sau ngy m cc thay i ny c hiu lc th i Tc c xem l chp thun cc thay i  v ng  tip tc thc hin Hp ng theo cc iu khon, iu kin mi. Cc Thng Bo, vn bn sa i, b sung, iu chnh Hp ng (nu c) s cu thnh mt phn khng th tch ri ca Hp ng v rng buc trch nhim vi Cc Bn.</td>\n                                </tr>\n\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td>4.6</td>\n                                    <td>Hp ng ny c hiu lc t ngy k v i Tc ng  rng KAFI c quyn chm dt cung cp mt phn hoc ton b cc Tin ch Lin Quan quy nh ti tng KK trong cc trng hp sau:</td>\n                                </tr>\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td>(a)</td>\n                                    <td>i Tc yu cu chm dt bng vn bn gi cho KAFI trc ngy d kin chm dt 03 (ba) Ngy Lm Vic, vi iu kin i Tc  thc hin xong tt c ngha v i vi KAFI;</td>\n                                </tr>\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td>(b)</td>\n                                    <td>i Tc vi phm Hp ng, hoc thc hin hnh vi b cm theo quy nh php lut m KAFI xt thy cn chm dt;</td>\n                                </tr>\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td>(c)</td>\n                                    <td>i Tc cht hoc b Ta n tuyn mt nng lc hnh vi dn s, mt tch, cht;
